![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/ee292cc7-8aae-40fc-b9fc-0608713ad630/17396.jpg?format=original)

Brock Lesnar opens Smackdown by attacking Michael Cole and Corey Graves.

Cole was going to do an interview with Lesnar but Lesnar would not wait. He picks up Cole and dumps him in the ring. Lesnar was going to presumably end Cole's life when Corey Graves got involved and took an F-5 for his efforts.

Security and agents run out but they couldn't stop Lesnar from hitting a second F-5.

He grabs the camera and screams for John Cena, then leaves.

