*   ## **_WWE Women's Tag Team Championships: Alexa Bliss and Charlotte Flair def. The Secret Her-vice_**
    

Miz joined Michael Cole at commentary to replace the late Corey Graves.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/f7e23782-8e75-4819-ab34-07b07bfaf651/17406.jpg?format=original)

B-Fab is trying to get the Street profits back together but Bo Dallas is in Angelo Dawkins ear asking him if Montez Ford really cares about him. Montez Ford grabs Uncle howdy by the neck but Eric Rowan takes the profits out.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/efcc44b4-b0f4-477b-b698-8097bc65e7d3/17412.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_Bron Breakker and Bronson Reed def. Fraxiom_** in a fun sprint
    

Fraxiom was in the ring for an unknown reason when the Brons attacked them. But Fraxiom wouldn't go down like some jobbers so they fought back and a match was made.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/d12e1fca-925b-489e-bca5-0bc9dc4a654d/17414.jpg?format=original)

The Usos let the Brons know that it's on tomorrow at Wrestlepalooza

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/3afb002a-94bb-4495-8a27-f90a16dd1967/17408.jpg?format=original)

R-Truth is backstage teaching wrestlers how to sign up for ESPN to watch Wrestlepalooza.

He puts his phone in a toaster.

