## **_Tiffany Stratton vs Nia Jax vs Jade Cargill for the WWE WOMEN'S CHAMPIONSHIP is officially on for next week on Smackdown!_**

Nia Jax was poking fun at both Jade and Tiffy when Tiffy came out.

Jade soon after her, busting right through security to get Nia Jax. Nick Aldis comes to th stage and makes the triple threat match official for next week's Smackdown

